snippet.title: How to Remove Spray Paint from a VANDALIZED Car
snippet.description:
Learn how to remove spray paint and overspray from your car's paint, plastic headlights, glass windows and windshield. If you get spray paint on your car, whether accidental overspray or because it was vandalized, this video will show you how to easily remove it using simple tools and products. I bought this vandalized car for a huge discount because it has spray paint all over the body, headlights, windshield, and windows so let me show you how to clean it off! And after this car is cleaned up, I am selling it on eBay and donating the proceeds to charity!

eBay Motors App: https://ebayvehicle.com/app/ChrisFix

Tools and Products I used:
Car Soap: https://amzn.to/2ZvnD9w
Clay Bar Kit: https://amzn.to/32pKQMj
Aggressive Clay Bar: https://amzn.to/3j3rgvg
Cleaner Wax: https://amzn.to/30sBMUz
Headlight UV Coating: https://amzn.to/2C6JBqR
Headlight Restoration Kit: https://amzn.to/3h3tPvq
Microfiber Towels: https://amzn.to/3ewbGVE
Microfiber Wash Mit: https://amzn.to/2B1bnEm

snippet.title: History Hijinks: Plague
snippet.description:
Escape the worries of our modern world by visiting the high middle ages and learning about something esoteric and irrelevant: Plague!
In this video, I attempt to actually teach you something about how the medieval world worked and how it responded to this existential threat, rather than dredging up 3rd grade plague facts for easy views. Oops, did I say that out loud?

SOURCES & Further Reading: "The Black Death: The World's Most Devastating Plague" via The Great Courses by Dorsey Armstrong, "From Plague Doctor to PPE" by Bernadette Banner (https://youtu.be/ZniriC-jTHg), "Biological Warfare at the Siege of Caffa" from the CDC (https://wwwnc.cdc.gov/eid/article/8/9/01-0536_article)

This video was edited by Sophia Ricciardi AKA "Indigo". https://www.sophiakricci.com/
Our content is intended for teenage audiences and up.

snippet.title: Ganas Que Te Tengo - Eslabon Armado - DEL Records 2020
snippet.description:
Eslabón Armado lanza “Vibras de Noche”, Descarga el disco completo de “VIbras De Noche” https://delrec.io/vibrasdenooche | Suscribete al canal oficial de Eslabon Armado https://bit.ly/3gc4rmJ | Suscribete al canal oficial de DEL Records https://bit.ly/2KIi2on su segunda producción bajo el sello de DEL Records. Y como plus, sorprenden con el video oficial del romántico tema: “Dame Tu Calor”

Después de posicionarse esta semana en el lugar numero 7 de compositores latinos según la revista Billboard, Pedro Tovar vocalista y compositor de Eslabón Armado, vuelve a sorprender de la mano DEL Records al presentarnos “Vibras de Noche”, su nueva producción discográfica, misma que podrás disfrutar a partir de hoy  viernes 17 de julio en todas las plataformas digitales.

Efectivamente, luego de la gran aceptación de “Tu Veneno Mortal”, material que debutó en #4 de iTunes en la música latina y que contiene éxitos como “Baby”, “Con Tus Besos” y “Me prendes”, entre otros, los chicos del área de la bahía no se durmieron en sus laureles y grabaron un nuevo material, con temas de corte romántico, alegres y urbanos, dedicados a chicos y grandes, que, como ellos, disfrutan del amor.

En “Vibras de Noche”, el grupo integrado por Pedro Ángel Tovar, Gabriel Hidalgo y Brayan Tovar, incluye canciones como “La Trokita”, canción cuyo vídeo, lanzado a principios de junio del presente año. Además, contiene los temas: “Dame tu Calor”, “Ganas que te tengo”, “Tal Vez”, “Tu Canción”, “Te quiero a ti”, “Amor” y “Romance”, todas escritas por el talentoso Pedro Ángel Tovar.

Síguenos:
Pandora: https://goo.gl/pb57i8
Spotify: https://goo.gl/nbrx8n
Instagram: https://goo.gl/RFknFr
Facebook: http://goo.gl/dDPjE1
Twitter:  https://goo.gl/Z6IVhF 
http://DelRecords.com

DEL Records, es la empresa líder independiente de entretenimiento de la música Regional Mexicana en Estados Unidos y México. Desde su lanzamiento en el 2009 la compañía ha creado un sin número de exitosos e innovadores artistas y canciones. Sus cantantes redefinen el género y se posicionan en los primeros lugares de las listas de popularidad, generando gran impacto en las redes sociales. DEL Records, DEL Publishing y DEL Entertainment, es la casa de grandes estrellas internacionales como Gerardo Ortiz, Regulo Caro, Ulices Chaidez y Sus Plebes al igual que otros grandes talentos como Lenin Ramirez, T3R Elemento, Los del Arroyo, Banda Culiacancito, Jaziel Avilez, Cheli Madrid, entre otros. La compañía fue establecida en el 2008.

#EslabonArmado #VibrasDeNoche #DELRecords

snippet.description:

Follow Joshua Bassett: 
http://joshuatbassett.com/
http://instagram.com/joshuatbassett
http://www.tiktok.com/@joshuatbassett
http://facebook.com/joshuatbassett

Directed by Joshua Bassett
Edited by Matt Sklar

Lyrics:
You say you gotta think it over
I can’t stop thinkin’ of you
Is he the guy you want to hold ya
I’ll be here when you need me to
 

Make you feel beautiful in the morning 
Light you up when the rain won’t stop pouring
Cause there’s a million little things I haven’t told ya
It kills me every time he’s with you so
 

How’m I supposed to think about anything else
How am I to go on keeping this to myself
I am done pretending I want anyone else
Anyone else
Anyone else
 

And now the days are getting longer
I’m caught daydreamin of you
I’m still waiting for my happy ever after
When you’re ready I’ll be ready too
So
 

How’m I supposed to think about anything else
How am I to go on keeping this to myself
I am done pretending I want anyone else
Anyone else
Anyone else
 

The world melts away when I’m with you
And I know you’re afraid to jump too soon
But I promise if you would
I’d love you better than he ever could
Girl we’d have it good, we’d have it good
 

How’m I supposed to think about anything else
How am I to go on keeping this to myself
I am done pretending I want anyone else
Anyone else
Anyone else
 

I keep hoping it’ll only be a matter of time
Till the memory fades and the feelings subside
Time won’t help I cant settle for anyone else
Anyone else
Anyone else

snippet.title: My Response To Fatphobia Claims
snippet.description:
I was scrolling through reddit today and came across this post saying I have “fatphobic tendencies”. This was really hard for me to read and caused me to take a critical look back at my previous comments regarding obesity, bariatric treatments, and diet recommendations (Keto, intermittent fasting, vegan, etc.) Our culture demonizes people for their weight, from rogue marketing pushing “ideal bodies” in media to a lack of representation for large bodied people on stage and on screen. That being said, I am a doctor, and my job is to help people live longer, healthier lives, and often those results can be achieved through a variety of tactics that will reduce the weight of people who suffer from obesity. It’s a fine line between helping my patients and making sure they don’t feel judged or criticized for the way they look, and I’m working hard to get it right.

ORIGINAL REDDIT POST: https://www.reddit.com/r/antidiet/comments/hq0lfh/i_really_want_to_like_dr_mike_on_youtube_but_he/?sort=top

COMMENTS ON BARIATRIC SURGERY REDDITOR REFERS TO: 
https://youtu.be/rh2FFCQ7QSs?t=406

RESEARCH ON OBESITY AND WEIGHT IN REGARDS TO HEALTH:
https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/books/NBK379120/
https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC5704829/#:~:text=Bariatric%20surgery%20has%20proved%20to,LAGB)%2C%20reported%20inconsistent%20results
https://www.cochrane.org/CD003641/ENDOC_surgery-for-obesity
https://uihc.org/health-topics/how-effective-bariatric-surgery

MY APPEARANCE ON PHIL DEFRANCO’S SHOW DISCUSSING FAT SHAMING: https://youtu.be/IdPFaDt2dEo?t=1367

MY NUTRITION PLAYLIST: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLJRbJuI_csVAMq2VPr96h6TL4Y98rfznM

I LOVE reading your comments and take your suggestions seriously. If there’s a subject you want me to discuss or something you’d like for me to react to, leave a comment down below. Many of my videos have been born out of suggestions directly from you, so don’t hold back!
-Doctor Mike Varshavski

snippet.title: The 1985 Effect
snippet.description:
The 1985 Effect - Now, saying that J. Cole was right might just be an understatement. 1985 by J. Cole is slowly over time becoming a reality many rappers are having to face. Lil Pump was of course the guy who the track was aimed at; but it's far from ''just a diss track''. 1985 is the guide for how your average young & popping rapper can avoid the pitfalls that come with being in that position. The effect is in fact - in full effect & both Lil Pump & Smokepurpp are the tangible proof. That's what I talk about. 

In this video I talk about the effect of 1985, by J. Cole.

snippet.title: CARA IS PREGNANT!!!
snippet.description:
WOW! Cara is pregnant! Completely unexpected surprise pregnancy. For Gemma and the Triplets we tried for a year with no success, and later found out she has PCOS and doesn't ovulate correctly, so she got medical help and took a pill (letrozole) to help her ovulate and it did the trick for both pregnancies. We figured that if we wanted to get pregnant again she would have to go on that pill again. We weren't opposed to having more kids, but definitely thought at least 2 years before she got back on it. So this came out of nowhere. We truly believe everything happens for a reason, and that this baby is supposed to be a part of our family. Those struggling with infertility, we have family members going through the same thing, and although we will never know why certain things happen, we just pray that you will still stay strong and positive. Never give up! We are so excited for baby number 5 to join us and so are the kids! Their reaction videos were all filmed prior to this since we have known for 3 weeks, and we will show those soon. The main question we have is will it be multiples again??? Twins? Another triplet pregnancy?! haha that would be absolutely insane, but you never what will happen around here anymore. Thanks for all the support you guys! We love each and every one of you!
